# Run this in your project root
cat > .gitmessage << 'EOF'
# <type>(<scope>): <short summary> (max 72 chars)
# |<----  Using a maximum of 72 characters  ---->|


# |<----   Leave a blank line, then body below  ---->|
# Explain WHY this change was made (not what — the diff shows that)


# |<----   Optional: footer for issues/breaking changes  ---->|
# Refs: #issue-number
# BREAKING CHANGE: describe what breaks and migration path

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# TYPE (pick one):
#   feat      → new feature
#   fix       → bug fix
#   chore     → tooling, deps, config (no logic change)
#   refactor  → restructure without behaviour change
#   test      → adding or fixing tests
#   docs      → readme, comments, docstrings
#   perf      → performance improvement
#   ci        → github actions, docker, deployment
#
# SCOPE (pick one for your project):
#   config        → core/config.py, .env
#   exceptions    → core/exceptions.py
#   github        → integrations/github/
#   storage       → storage/
#   models        → models/
#   schemas       → schemas/
#   dao           → data_access/
#   services      → services/
#   api           → api/
#   rag           → rag/
#   vectorstore   → vectorstore/
#   embeddings    → providers/embeddings/
#   llm           → providers/llm/
#   parser        → providers/parser/
#   chunking      → services/chunking.py
#   intelligence  → intelligence/
#   frontend      → frontend/
#   docker        → Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml
#   deps          → requirements.txt, package.json
#   migrations    → migrations/
#   tests         → any test file
#
# EXAMPLES:
#   feat(github): add GitHubService clone and pull methods
#   fix(cloner): delete partial clone directory on failure
#   chore(deps): add gitpython pathspec to requirements.txt
#   refactor(api): extract error handling into middleware
#   test(ingestion): add smoke tests for ingest endpoint
#   feat(embeddings): add sentence-transformers provider
#   ci(docker): add postgres service to docker-compose
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
EOF